headline: Workday Rising to Feature Star-Studded Lineup With Brené Brown, Duran Duran, and Microsoft
summary: Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ: WDAY), the AI platform for managing people, money, and agents, today announced its talent, customer and partner headliners, and partner sponsors at Workday Rising 2025, the company's annual flagship conference for finance, HR, and IT professionals taking place September 15-18 in San Francisco. Workday Rising 2025 is where the future of work comes into focus, showcasing bold ideas and powerful innovations designed to help organizations manage their people, money, and AI age
